{"tid":200072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有女仔問左我一個我唔撚知點答嘅問題","createTime":"2017-04-13T16:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T16:28:59.000Z","uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"991b25122c0bdfff2cca28222e26a995b6f745a0","tid":200072,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"佢話 點解有啲叔父寧願留個地中海頭留到barcode咁拉左拉右咁7<br />\n都唔肯直接剃光/skin head<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同佢講 男人要接受自己無頭髮<br />\n類似就係主動除晒衫出街 尊嚴問題 <br />\n答完佢好似仲係好撚唔滿意/理解<br />\n屌我老味 我都唔知仲可以點解釋<br />\n關鳩我事咩 我不知幾撚多頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打有類似經驗或者諗法<br />\n或者絲打有同樣疑問 可以解釋多啲究竟你唔明個位係乜"},{"pid":"68aa98ba96447a11ffcdd5286c899566ef5bfcda","tid":200072,"uid":52362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔明<br />\n光頭肯定型過地中海啦"},{"pid":"cc81c54d23c8a67b8b27d0d3666ff88cd7a118d0","tid":200072,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"同埋男人少/甚至無腳毛佢又話好羨慕 屌 佢唔撚知啲人比人笑白切雞 女人腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db93d277ec1bc352bd802635e1a2616d03f25a84","tid":200072,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:12:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都唔明<br />\n光頭肯定型過地中海啦</blockquote><br />\n或者人地頭型唔靚呢屌 講真呢啲各人品味<br />\n佢問我 我盡解 又無標準答案 可以點同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a8587ee7f97a46e071e1c627da42e6437181d6","tid":200072,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"我家族禿頭，自己應該走唔甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預咗有一日會剷光晒啲頭髮"},{"pid":"a5ecc8cb44e334bc38d7c0591a6901a3227655fd","tid":200072,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我家族禿頭，自己應該走唔甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預咗有一日會剷光晒啲頭髮</blockquote><br />\n定係會留邊skin head咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c57952dfce65da20a31d728bcf941c7c3965de","tid":200072,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"有無啲可以秒回嘅答法"},{"pid":"42dca9f660ad5bd672c12a760278454bc1b4015d","tid":200072,"uid":11515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"因為禿頭既人唔係一晚之間變地中海，<br />\n成個地中海可能歷時20年，<br />\n所以中間既心態轉變會係習慣，接受。<br />\n<br />\n如果一晚變禿我諗大部份人都會剷"},{"pid":"a103c93b57fa75d4527ca9e4aa5f9e18899c499e","tid":200072,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為禿頭既人唔係一晚之間變地中海，<br />\n成個地中海可能歷時20年，<br />\n所以中間既心態轉變會係習慣，接受。<br />\n<br />\n如果一晚變禿我諗大部份人都會剷</blockquote><br />\n呢樣佢都有提 佢講得好撚mean<br />\n話咁禿緊你都明知唔會生番<br />\n長痛不如短痛 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}